      "title": "Senior citizen in fuel queue dies \u2013 15th such death so far",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Another Sri Lankan senior citizen died while waiting in line for fuel.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said a 63-year-old man who was in line for fuel in Payagala had suddenly fallen ill and was rushed to hospital where he was ruled dead upon admission.",
        "The post-mortem examination is to be conducted today, and this is the 15th death to have taken place at a fuel queue, reported by News 1st so far."
      ],
